  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494720/extras/34c5d0fd4c442992663bef1b86c91734.avif?t=1692204442\" width=528 height=68 /></span><br><strong>Little Man woke up and doesn't know what to do with his day. </strong><br>Play as Little Man and help him through the day by walking around and talking to friends (or foes) in this short and silly game about feeling 'eh'.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494720/extras/5c69ea1e99bf1a6a8dbd329e3bee5a00.avif?t=1692204442\" width=310 height=190 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494720/extras/372da589461b6045618848f71e714476.webp?t=1692204442\" width=241 height=63 /></span><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A narrative driven 2D walking sim!</li><li>Short! (~15 minutes)</li><li>Handwritten journal to read!</li><li> 8 Steam achievements for people who care! </li></ul></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2494720/extras/21d43eaa86de13b31b87924ae1defea6.avif?t=1692204442\" width=370 height=190 /></span>",
